title: [Solhaven, Changeling and Murre]
[Solhaven, Changeling Bending]
description: Flooding the intersection with the light streaming from its windows as well as the aroma of baked goods from its door, a modest-sized building stands on the northwest corner.  Customers enter in ones and twos and leave with cookies, muffins and small loaves in hand.

A modest-sized building stained a pale yellow with dark blue trim around the windows and powder blue awnings sits on the northwest corner, the mouthwatering aroma of fresh baked goods wafting from its open door.  A pair of pushcart vendors are loading up with golden brown loaves just outside, their efforts constantly impeded by the flow of customers in and out of the entrance.

Flooding the intersection with the light streaming from its windows as well as the aroma of baked goods from its door, a modest-sized building stands on the northwest corner, where it overlooks the waters of the Sunderer's Glaive.  Customers enter in ones and twos and leave with cookies, muffins and small loaves in hand.

A modest-sized building, stained a pale yellow with dark blue trim around the windows and powder blue awnings, sits on the northwest corner, overlooking the waters of the Glaive. The mouthwatering aroma of fresh baked goods wafts from its open door.  A pair of pushcart vendors are loading up with golden brown loaves just outside, their efforts constantly impeded by the flow of customers in and out of the entrance.
